{"type": "article", "id": 2298, "title": "YOHANN  iPad 支架", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T23:50:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052223385WT9rgfvukR2zItd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞士建筑设计师 Berend Frenzel 近日设计了一款名为“ YOHANN ”的 iPad 支架，从不同的位置和角度带来不同的功能。YOHANN 看上去只是一个再简洁不过的支架，但它却可以从 3 个不同的角度支好 iPad，满足用户无论是坐着、站着或是躺着都能拥有适合的角度。目前，YOHANN 有两个版本在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/808720883/yohann-the-different-stand-for-the-ipad\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上众筹，一种是表面涂有高端钢琴漆的玻璃纤维加固塑料机身，报价 69 美元；另一种是木质版本，报价 129 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222334BfhILTQjD38zsPeg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222335AV10tj9o6PM8sIOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222335Z0RUArFVYWmceHCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222336hLY1IV0AuPbSzZKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222337FHJulMGiDm90KYcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}